The Perfect Potato.

This recipe prints out the word Potato.

Ingredients.
111 ml milk
116 ml cream
97 ml oil
116 ml water
111 ml vinegar
80 ml broth

Method.
Put milk into the mixing bowl.
Put cream into the mixing bowl.
Put oil into the mixing bowl.
Put water into the mixing bowl.
Put vinegar into the mixing bowl.
Put broth into the mixing bowl.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.

Servings 1.
